    <div class="mb-1 flex items-start gap-3">
      <img src="/logos/github.png" alt="GitHub" class="w-14 h-14 shrink-0 mt-0.5 object-contain" />
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">GitHub</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Software Engineer, Copilot CLI</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-faint mt-0.5">Jun 2026 – Present · Seattle, WA · <span class="italic">Dual-Access Employee (Weekends)</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
      <li class="text-[15px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Selected to contribute open source to <a href="https://github.com/github/copilot-cli" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-muted transition-colors">GitHub Copilot CLI</a> as a Microsoft Dual-Access Employee. Contributing on weekends.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
      <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 bg-surface border border-border-subtle rounded font-mono text-text-faint">TypeScript</span>
      <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 bg-surface border border-border-subtle rounded font-mono text-text-faint">Rust</span>
      <span class="text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 bg-surface border border-border-subtle rounded font-mono text-text-faint">GitHub</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="my-10 border-border-subtle" />

  <!-- Microsoft AI & Infra -->
  <section>
    <div class="mb-1 flex items-start gap-3">
      <img src="/logos/microsoft.png" alt="Microsoft" class="w-14 h-14 shrink-0 mt-0.5 object-contain" />
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Microsoft</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Software Engineer, AI & Infrastructure</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-faint mt-0.5">Aug 2025 – Present · Seattle, WA</p>
